<p><span class="script">gecko_callout_heading("1.9")</span></p>
<p>Prior to Gecko 1.9 <span class="script">geckoRelease("1.9")</span>, disabling tabs fails; even while disabled, it still accepts events.</p>
</div>
<p>Also, "unhiding" a tab leads to unpredictable ordering of the tabs. See <span class="script">Bug(307088)</span> and <span class="script">Bug(261826)</span>. Use <span class="script">xulattr("collapsed")</span> instead of <span class="script">xulattr("hidden")</span>.</p>
